_id": "sub-cap-math", "paper_id": "cap-109-math", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "計算 2 x 2 − 3 除以 x + 1 後，得商式和餘式分別為何？", "options": ["商式為 2，餘式為 −5", "商式為 2 x − 5，餘式為 5", "商式為 2 x + 2，餘式為 −1", "商式為 2 x − 2，餘式為 −1"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "551f42c20633", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64e8d2b7d3a1", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 7, "raw_text": "7.   計算 2 x 2 − 3 除以 x + 1 後，得商式和餘式分別為何？\n     (A) 商式為 2，餘式為 −5\n     (B) 商式為 2 x − 5，餘式為 5\n     (C) 商式為 2 x + 2，餘式為 −1\n     (D) 商式為 2 x − 2，餘式為 −1\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-math-008", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-math", "paper_id": "cap-109-math", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "下列何者可表示成兩個質數的乘積？", "options": ["81", "82", "83", "84"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "551f42c20633", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64e8d2b7d3a1", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 8, "raw_text": "8.   下列何者可表示成兩個質數的乘積？\n     (A) 81\n     (B) 82\n     (C) 83\n     (D) 84\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-math-009", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-math", "paper_id": "cap-109-math", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "已知小薇住家的西方 100 公尺處為車站，住家的北方 200 公尺處為學校，且\n從學校往東方走 100 公尺，再往南方走 400 公尺可到達公園。若小薇將住家、\n車站、學校分別標示在坐標平面上的 ( 2 , 0 )、 ( 0 , 0 )、 ( 2 , 4 ) 三點，則公園\n應標示在此坐標平面上的哪一點？\n(A) ( 4 , −4 )\n(B) ( 4 , 12 )\n(C) ( 0 , −4 )\n(